OL,6,FBy ITV News Central Production
OL,7,FJournalist Laurence Griffin
OL,9,FA sales rep who was seen on CCTV being
OL,10,Frobbed in Birmingham's Jewellery
OL,11,FQuarter said the area has become "very
OL,12,Fdangerous" for people working there.
OL,14,FThe Jewellery Quarter is home to over
OL,15,Fa hundred retailers and diamond
OL,16,Fdealers, and produces around 40% of
OL,17,Fthe UK's jewellery.
