OL,6,FPeople working there have told ITV
OL,7,FNews Central thieves are targeting
OL,8,Fthem as they walk the streets of the
OL,9,FJewellery Quarter, rather than trying
OL,10,Fto steal from shops armed with CCTV
OL,11,Fand heavy locked doors.
OL,13,FOne of those is Arthur - not his real
OL,14,Fname - who is a jewellery sales rep
OL,15,Fwho wished to remain anonymous.
OL,17,FHe was attacked in the heart of the
OL,18,FJewellery Quarter in 2023 by a man who
OL,19,Fpunched him several times in the head
OL,20,Fbefore driving off with the bags of
OL,21,Fjewellery he was carrying.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
