OL,6,FArthur said: "I will never forget that
OL,7,Fday. I was shaking, everything went in
OL,8,Fslow motion, it was one of the most
OL,9,Fsurreal experiences.
OL,11,F"I was in absolute hysterics, I was
OL,12,Fshouting for help, running down the
OL,13,Froad looking for somebody to come to
OL,14,Fmy aid."
OL,16,FArthur has to be insured by an agency
OL,17,Fto work as a jewellery rep, but making
OL,18,Fa claim has made his premium rise.
