OL,6,FHe has been told if he has another
OL,7,Fincident within five years he could
OL,8,Fbecome too expensive to insure, and
OL,9,Flose his livelihood.
OL,11,FSeveral people working in the
OL,12,FJewellery Quarter have reported gangs
OL,13,Ftargeting people as they go home or as
OL,14,Fthey bring jewellery into shops.
OL,16,FOne shop owner said she was followed
OL,17,Fhome after locking up for the night,
OL,18,Fand robbed on her driveway.
