OL,6,FArthur said: "It's easier for
OL,7,F(thieves) to target somebody outside
OL,8,Fthan go into a shop and target a shop
OL,9,Fwhere there are cameras aplenty.
OL,11,F"When you've got someone with a
OL,12,Ftrolley walking around in the streets
OL,13,Fof the Jewellery Quarter they're easy
OL,14,Fprey for these people who can just
OL,15,Fpull up in a car, snatch your bag and
OL,16,Fdrive off within seconds."
OL,18,FHe believes the area has become less
OL,19,Fsafe after the police station on Vyse
OL,20,FStreet was closed by West Midlands
OL,21,FPolice in 2017.
