OL,6,FHe said: "I've been coming to the
OL,7,FJewellery Quarter for over 20 years
OL,8,Fnow, and back then it was relatively
OL,9,Fsafe, there was a police station here
OL,10,Fso if anything happened police were on
OL,11,Fthe scene within seconds.
OL,13,F"Over the last three or four years it
OL,14,Fhas become very dangerous to carry
OL,15,Fjewellery around the Quarter because
OL,16,Fthere are a lot of gangs targeting
OL,17,Fagents.
