OL,6,FSunny Pal, Director of jewellery shop
OL,7,FAstella & Co, said: "It's mainly the
OL,8,Fwholesalers carrying suitcases around
OL,9,Fwith jewellery pieces getting targeted
OL,10,Fmore with people sat in cars watching
OL,11,Fthem walk around in different
OL,12,Fjewellery shops, but some owners are
OL,13,Falso being targeted now.
OL,15,F"There are people getting nails put
OL,16,Fbehind their cars so when they drive
OL,17,Fout their tyre will puncture and
OL,18,Fthey'll have to stop and that's when
OL,19,Fpeople come out and approach the car."
